ge student known for her cute face.\n- One day, the Matsuda rescues her from a crisis.\n- Since that day, Miyuki starts following Ken around, showing her affection...\n\n**\u2665 Key Features \u2665**\n- 100% full voice acting (Korean, Japanese)\n- Various manga-like 2D cutscenes\n\nExperience unforgettable love in LOVE ON!\n\n\nMiyuki CV(JP) : Monaca Morino\n\nMiyuki CV(KO) : Jimin\n\n\u24d2Songasonga / Novelpia Ltd.", "short_description": "Become the main character in a romantic comedy game.\nSet against the backdrop of a fresh summer, the beautiful love story between two people begins now."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://looksten.com/privacy-policy-loveon-first/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Looksten Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://looksten.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3771364559549515"}, {"id": "2691890164460465"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ko", "ja", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7872434239529125"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "374490005597951"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "374490005597951"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1726791241, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "374490005597951"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id